Should we change variable name to tid and eid to make the code consistence with other codes in libpldm?

I mean `terminus_id` to `tid`. Like below code
https://github.com/openbmc/libpldm/blob/main/src/transport/transport.c#L62C10-L62C24

About `instance_id` some code use `iid` but in transport.c/h we are using instance_id. So `instance_id` is fine to me.
